             was indicted for <rs id="t18310908-281-off1440" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-281-off1440" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-281-off1440" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on <rs id="t18310908-281-cd1441" type="crimeDate">10th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-281-off1440 t18310908-281-cd1441"></join>, 1 reticule, value 2d.; 1 purse, value 2d.; 1 crown, and 11 shillings, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18310908-281-victim2045" type="victimName">
                        Mary Anne 
                        Williams
                     <interp inst="t18310908-281-victim2045" type="surname" value="Williams"></interp>
